query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(DISTINCT sessionId) as total_sessions,
  COUNT(DISTINCT userId) as unique_users,
  COUNT(*) as total_events
FROM events;

SELECT 
  eventType,
  COUNT(*) as event_count,
  COUNT(DISTINCT sessionId) as sessions_with_event
FROM events
GROUP BY eventType
ORDER BY event_count DESC;
